Troy Flake doesn't take a passive approach to personal injury. As a former federal prosecutor, he's built a career around holding people accountable. That same intensity applies to insurance companies, negligent drivers, and anyone else responsible for your injuries.

We handle cases throughout Henderson, Las Vegas, and all of Southern Nevada — from car accidents on the Strip to slip-and-fall injuries in local businesses. If someone else's negligence caused your injuries, we fight for the compensation you deserve.
